disk command
compare

solaris:
(1) show disk:
    format

(2) partition disk
    1. format
       -> fdisk
       -> partition
          -> label
          -> quit
       -> label

(3) format partition
    newfs /dev/rdsk/c231t231d1s0
    disk is c231t231d1
    s0 is partition0

(4) mount partition
    mount /dev/dsk/c231t231d1s0 /test
    must use dsk, not rdsk

(5) check disk io performance
    iostat -xn 5
